Nói Albinói;;85;;87;;PG-13;;Seventeen-year-old Nói (Tómas Lemarquis), an albino, lives with his grandmother, Lina (Anna Fridriksdottir), in an isolated town in Iceland. Bright but bored with a life that offers no possibility of change or excitement, Nói amuses himself by antagonizing teachers and administrators at school, which angers his father, Kiddi (Þröstur Leó Gunnarsson). His daily routine is brightened by the arrival of Iris (Elin Hansdottir), a young gas station attendant Nói dreams of running away with.;;Drama;;Dagur Kári;;2003;;Tómas Lemarquis,Þröstur Leó Gunnarsson,Elin Hansdottir,Anna Fridriksdottir,Hjalti Rognvaldsson,Petur Einarsson,Kjartan Bjargmundsson,Greipur Gislason;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/noi-the-albino